snippet.title: Finding an Exterior Angle in a Polygon
snippet.description:
Learn how to find an exterior angle in a polygon in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.  We go through 2 examples one regular and one irregular polygon.

0:12 Example 1 Find the Exterior Angle of the Polygon
0:23 What the Exterior Angles Sum To
1:27 Example 2 What is the Exterior Angle in a Regular Octagon
1:32 What is a Regular Polygon
1:39 Formula for Finding One of the Exterior Angles in a Regular Polygon

Related Videos:
